Package: clairvoyant
Type: R
Title: Forecasting demand with calendar time effects
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Amy Richardson
Maintainer: Amy Richardson <amy.richardson.phd@gmail.com>
Description: Forecasts demand (long and short term rolling forecast) for Crisp takehome test. Also computes key merics such as product delivery volume, age, delivery precision, revenue and profit. Produces key graphics to detail the results.
